OL,3,CJersey Rugby Club secure promotion
OL,4,Cafter nineteenth straight win
OL,6,FJersey Rugby Club have secured
OL,7,Fpromotion following this afternoon's
OL,8,F(7 March) win over Bracknell RFC.
OL,10,FThe Channel Island team have a perfect
OL,11,Frecord so far this seaon, with today's
OL,12,Fvictory making it 19 consecutive wins
OL,13,Fin the league.
OL,15,FThis afternoon's match in Berkshire
OL,16,Fended 38 - 7, meaning Jersey were also
OL,17,Fcrowned league champions with three
OL,18,Fgames still to play.
