OL,3,CJersey Rugby Club secure promotion
OL,4,Cafter nineteenth straight win
OL,6,FJersey will now play in the National
OL,7,FLeagues next season and compete at the
OL,8,Fsame level as Guernsey Raiders.
OL,10,FHowever, we will not know whether our
OL,11,Fisland rivals will be pitted against
OL,12,Feach other in the same league for 2026
OL,13,F/ 27 until later this summer.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
